name: Cary Reams
text: The Pass aux Heron is a natural channel, slightly deeper than the surrounding waters, which crosses the Mississippi Sound under the Dauphin Island Bridge and into the Mobile Bay. The bridge here is actually quite cool and a tad bit steep!  It offers a fantastic view as you drive over or boat under it!  I am super surprised there aren’t more photos or posts of this area - guess I’ll have to kick it up a notch the next time I’m out this way!!!!
